content.rendered:
Directed by Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari

Written by Nikhil Mehrotra. Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari. Nitesh Tiwari. Nitesh Tiwari. Amit Joshi

Cast Kangana Ranaut (Jaya Nigam Sachdeva). Jassie Gill (Prashant Sachdeva). Richa Chadha (Meenu). Neena Gupta (Rachna Nigam). Yagya Bhasin (Aditya ‘Aadi’). Megha Burman (Nisha Daas). Rajesh Tailang (National Coach Sinha). Deepak Agarwal (Clerk). Smita Dwivedi (Smita Tambe). Backagaindancer (Rahul verma). Cricknowle (Bhai Jaan). Manoj Jadhav (Selection Executive). Rohit Modi (Van Driver). Yusof Mutahar (Trainer). Umair Patel (Musical Artist (archive sound)). Piyush Seetha (Piyush). Manish Soni (Jaya Nigam’s Frind)

Languages Hindi

Producers Syed Zaid Ali. Zohaib Ali. Prasanna R. Coondapur. Manoj Jadhav. Siva Konar. Amit Kothari. Navmeet Singh.

Production Fox STAR Studios. FoxStarHindi
